  @edge-case @observability
  Scenario: The on_flag callback fires for flagged turns
    Given the MCP server is booted with the logger-only on_flag callback wired
    When a turn is flagged for review (over-budget, exhausted, or fallback)
    Then a structured log line tagged orchestrator_turn_flagged should be
